Then, use the 'growth serum' (ğŸŒ¡ï¸) once or twice; it often boosts the value significantly (e.g., to 25 or 30). Crucially, apply the 'mutation catalyst' (ğŸ§¬) to this grown item. It will likely drop the value to -5. Immediately apply the 'mutation catalyst' *again* to that negative-valued item, and it should jump to 55! Be careful: applying tools to an item already at 55 or one that has been mutated twice often causes the value to plummet. You can repeat this process with a second pair of ingredients to have a backup or a chance to exceed 55. Good luck!
